# CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md

## Code of Conduct

### 1. Be Respectful
Everyone should be treated with respect. No harassment, discrimination, or offensive behavior.

### 2. Be Inclusive
Everyone is welcome to contribute. Differences in perspectives are valued.

### 3. Report Issues
If you encounter any violations, please report them to the maintainers.

By contributing, you agree to abide by this code of conduct.
